float get_noise(vec2 pos, float scale, int octaves, float persistence, float lacunarity) {
    float frequency = scale;
    float amplitude = 1.0;
    float total_amplitude = 0.0;
    float sum = 0.0;

    for (int octave = 0; octave < octaves; ++octave) {
        sum += opensimplex_noise(pos * frequency) * amplitude;
        total_amplitude += amplitude;

        frequency *= lacunarity;
        amplitude *= persistence;
    }
    return sum / total_amplitude;
}
```

上面的 `get_noise` 函数实现了周期，持续性和连续性的支持，类似于 Godot 中的 OpenSimplexNoise 类。要与 Godot 中的默认参数一致，请使用以下默认参数调用函数：

